com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Interface ReadServiceEntrySheetsService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultReadServiceEntrySheetsService

    public interface ReadServiceEntrySheetsService

    This service enables a remote system to read service entry sheets from SAP S4/HANA tenant. The remote system calls the sychronous OData service API_SERVICE_ENTRY_SHEET.

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_SERVICE_ENTRY_SHEET_SRV
    API Version:1
    Minimum ERP Version:1708
    Communication Scenario:Service Entry Sheet Integration (SAP_COM_0146)
    Scope Items:Service and Material Procurement - Project-Based Services (J13)
